title: Divine Heresy - Bleed the Fifth (2007)
description:
This is another good Death Metal album, although I must note the entire album isn&#039;t death metal.  There are one or two songs that are a little lighter, and the singer uses a softer voice at points, but nevertheless it&#039;s a good album.  If you like Fear Factory and Cannibal Corpse, Brain Drill, Decapitated, or Hatebreed, you&#039;ll enjoy this CD.
